        <section>
            <title>Packet object that is sent via the radios</title>
      <description>
<para>This is the object that is passed to the radio to be sent. It has the source/destination address, a counter, and the payload inside. </para>
</description>
            <para>
                <itemizedlist>
                    <listitem>
                        <para>uint8_t address</para>
